EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 021000Z TO 022000Z OCT
   WITHIN 60 MILES OF 57-02.0N 009-07.4W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 022100Z OCT.
